Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.54,0:00:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, anybody have any questions? We'll proceed.\NOkay, that's the question line, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.90,0:00:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, my question is, when you mentioned early on...\NOkay, just speak normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, 15% of people on the planet are above, like, 200.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.44,0:00:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, just curious, if that isn't set in stone, is it?\NOr if that's been increasing, and that increasing is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.22,0:00:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said during the lecture, the consciousness level of mankind at the time of the birth of Buddha was 90.\NAt the time of the birth of Jesus Christ, the consciousness level of mankind was at 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.50,0:01:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it evolved to 190, yes, 190, over the centuries, 1200s, 1300s, Middle Ages, until the late 1980s.\NAbout 1987, at about the time of the Harmonic Accordance, it suddenly jumped from 190 to 205.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.88,0:01:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I understood that, but is that due to a higher percentage of people being above 200?\NI mean, you could have just a different distribution to cause the overall average...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.30,0:01:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I can tell you, the collective consciousness, that's what it calibrates at.\NOkay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:02:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, besides maintaining unconditional love, compassion, and compassion,\Nkindness in everything you do, is there other things you can do to help protect from appearances of the lower astral realm?
