Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There are those dark...\NYes, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides maintaining unconditional love and compassion and kindness,\Nis there anything else you can do to help protect yourself from their appearances?
