Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.\NBesides, you know, everybody has karma, righto?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.44,0:02:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.\NAll the people you strangle to death, and you don't think you're going to choke some night, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. So we've got to figure it ourselves, too.\NAccept your karma with good graces.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.\NYou know, I would pray, that's all. You just pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.\NAnd there are many invocations, you know, and the white light and all those kind of things, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Thank you.\NBesides, that which is negative hates that which is positive,
